       >>SOURCE FORMAT FREE
IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. FACTCOBOL.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 ARG-COUNT        PIC S9(9) COMP-5 VALUE 0.
01 ARG-TEXT         PIC X(64) VALUE SPACES.
01 N                PIC 9(18) COMP-5 VALUE 99999.
01 RETCODE          PIC S9(9) COMP-5 VALUE 0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PARA.
    ACCEPT ARG-COUNT FROM ARGUMENT-NUMBER
    IF ARG-COUNT > 0 THEN
        ACCEPT ARG-TEXT FROM ARGUMENT-VALUE
        COMPUTE N = FUNCTION NUMVAL(ARG-TEXT)
    END-IF

    CALL "bench_cobol" USING BY VALUE N RETURNING RETCODE
    STOP RUN.
